4:[["$","p",null,{"children":"AI Coach System is a Django-based artificial intelligence-powered study coach web application designed to help users work more efficiently."}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"The system includes user authentication and profile management to store personalized data. Google's Gemini API is integrated via the google-genai SDK, specifically using the gemini-2.0-flash model, to generate dynamic and personalized study recommendations based on user inputs."}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"The AI logic is isolated into a dedicated service layer for modularity. Error handling and prompt engineering improvements enhance both system stability and response quality."}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"The goal is to develop an intelligent, scalable, and real-world-ready AI-powered education assistant that creates smart study plans tailored to a student's goals and daily study duration. Future plans include advanced personalization, data tracking, and integration with different AI models."}]]
